                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The amalgamite is hit by a Strike</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The amalgamite Repositions itself or Transposes itself with another creature. If the amalgamite successfully Transposes its location, it and any transposed creature take half damage from the triggering Strike.</p>"
