            "sort": 1000000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The amalgamite chooses up to two destabilized creatures it can see within 50 feet and swaps their positions, or moves one such creature to an unoccupied space it can see within range. If the amalgamite chooses two creatures, it can choose itself as a target, but both targets must be the same size. An unwilling creature can attempt a @Check[will|dc:33] save. If either target succeeds at this saving throw, both are unaffected.</p>"
                },
